<blockquote>
<p>But isn't it explicitly stated on this page that they don't do decommissions anymore?</p>
</blockquote>
<p>You'd be surprised how many people don't read page headings. d: Also, there's no guarantee someone will read the page heading to begin with, if they're mainly interested in looking at -D articles.</p>
<blockquote>
